(a) Эхлээд нимгэн бөмбөрцөг давхаргыг авч үзье of radius $\rho$ ба mass $\delta M$. energy of interaction of particle with an elementary belt $\delta S$ of that layer is equal to (Зур. 8)
\begin{equation*}
d U=-\gamma(m \delta M / 2 л) \sin \theta d \theta. \tag{*}
\end{equation*}
According to cosine theorem in triangle OAP $л^{2}=\rho^{2}+ +r^{2}-2 \rho r \cos \theta$. Having determined differential of this expression, we can reduce Eq. (*) to form that is convenient for integration. After integrating over whole layer we obtain $\delta U= =-\gamma m \delta M / r$. ба finally, integrating over all layers of sphere, we obtain $U=-\gamma m M / r$; (b) $F_{r}=-\partial U / \partial r=-\gamma m M / r^{2}$.

$А=-\frac{3}{2} \gamma m M / R$.
$$
\text { 1.214. } \begin{aligned}
G & =\left\{\begin{array}{л}
-\left(\gamma M / R^{3}\right) \mathrm{r} \text { for } r \leqslant R,
-\left(\gamma M / r^{3}\right) \mathrm{r} \text { for } r \geqslant R;
-3 / 2\left(1-r^{2} / 3 R^{2}\right) \gamma M / R \text { for } r \leqslant R,
-\gamma M / r
\end{array}\right.
\end{aligned}
$$

statement.value:
Бодис үүсэх таталцлын харилцан үйлчлэлийн зохистой потенциал энерги
(a) $m$ масстай, $R$ радиустай нимгэн жигд бөмбөрцөг давхарга;
(б) $m$ масстай, $R$ радиустай нэгэн жигд бөмбөрцөг (1.214-р асуудлын хариултыг ашиглана уу).
